Source.Name: gnote
Source.Summary: A simple and easy to use desktop note-taking application
Source.Description: Gnote is a simple note-taking application for GNOME desktop environment. It allows you to capture your ideas, link them together using WikiWiki-style links, group together in notebooks and some extra features for everyday use.
